    "notes": "LAN multicast handles one subnet. Home/workshop/travel/phone nodes should use same-LAN, hotspot, a self-hosted WireGuard/private tunnel, or the authenticated relay. Raw public forwarding is a last resort; never expose the Hive node API or local dashboard directly to the internet. Public hive participation is disabled until stronger sandbox, identity, and abuse controls exist."
